        "text_QzBrVP": {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "t:names.text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>A recognized Florida Brand for over 20 years!</p><p>If you’re looking to carry a great coffee with some home grown Florida flair, Latitude 23.5  Coffee & Tea is the brand for you. Our coffee staff has more than 90 years of professional coffee experience, from cafes to roasting, packing and green coffee buying, even grocery - Someone on our staff has done it. So whether you are a start-up cafe needing a little hand holding, a restaurant looking for a true espresso, a hotel looking for single serve, or a grocery looking for a Florida brand we can help.</p>",
            "width": "fit-content",
