              "blocks": {
                "text_tEiwMA": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>With 20 years of coffee roasting experience, we can help you create a shelf-ready coffee product in just weeks. Thanks to our facilities and professionals, we can package your coffee into bags (1.5oz to 5 lb), K-Cups,  and more, grind to your exact specifications, and toll roast your green coffee.</p><p>We offer a variety of house blend coffees and an outstanding line-up of espressos with flavor profiles to fit any tastes.  Our flavored coffee options can further entice your taste buds.</p><p>We also do custom blending and profile development using your coffee or ours.</p><p>To get started, just contact us and we'll be there to assist you along the way!</p>",
